extendedInfo.description: Date Nation is a leading dating community website with over 40million members. Date Nation enables you to to meet friends, find love, chat and have fun. Thousands of people just like you are joining Date Nation every day!Find dates, romance, companionship and fun - join today!What are you waiting for? DateNation is free to join.At Date Nation it is as easy as possible to meet people, you'll find a community of people looking to make connections and find partners for dating, love, romance, friendship, fun and other encounters. Date Nation allows you to find exactly the kind of person you are looking for. Standard member, you can: - chat- send private messages- browse through profiles- read interactive magazine, post or answer questions, post articles or poetry There's plenty to do as a Standard member! To speed up your search, you can consider one of the premium memberships which offer far more privileges and cost only as little as 25 cents per day (or less).Membership system enables Date Nation to keep data files that contain your profile information and other information as your Hotlist, etc. As a guest you can enter the site and browse through listings, but in order to post a listing and use several other features, you must join and become a member.Date Nation only requires a valid email address in order for you become a member. Password is sent to email address provided.
